      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUKA DONCIC NZ (12) finished fifth last start, beaten 3 metres at this track over 1660m when well supported. Draws out a little on the second line and may need luck at some point. Facing a tougher assignment but he is capable of running a big race. WARRAWEE FLYER (1) scored at this track three runs ago when leading all of the way. Returned to something like that form last time out when third over 1660m at this track, beaten 1.4 metres. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position and is good enough to take this race out. MY ULTIMATE COSSIE (3) is in the mix following a fourth at his most recent appearance over 2138m at this track after sitting outside the leader. BETTOR CHEER NZ (9) after a last stat third at this track is also in contention, although the draw makes his job a bit tougher. Has placed in all of his last four runs and is a must include in exotic bets.",
